# 抖音内容发布前检查清单 / Douyin Pre-Publish Checklist

## Account Analysis Review / 账号分析检查

### Target Audience Analysis / 目标受众分析

Before creating content, verify:
- [ ] Target demographic is clear (age/gender/location)
- [ ] Audience pain points identified
- [ ] Audience interests documented
- [ ] Best posting times determined
- [ ] Engagement patterns analyzed

### Content Positioning / 内容定位

- [ ] Niche/category is well-defined
- [ ] Unique value proposition is clear
- [ ] Content themes are consistent
- [ ] Differentiation from competitors is clear
- [ ] Personal brand style is established

---

## Viral Content Deconstruction / 爆款内容拆解检查

### Top 10 Analysis / 前10爆款分析

For each viral video analyzed:
- [ ] Hook (0-3s) is documented
- [ ] Content structure is mapped
- [ ] Visual elements are listed
- [ ] Audio elements are noted
- [ ] Engagement triggers identified
- [ ] CTA strategy is analyzed
- [ ] Success factors are extracted

### Pattern Recognition / 模式识别

- [ ] Common themes across top videos identified
- [ ] Recurring formats noted
- [ ] Consistent elements documented
- [ ] Unique factors (X-factors) found
- [ ] Replicable patterns extracted

---

## Copy Creation Checklist / 文案创作检查

### Title Quality / 标题质量

- [ ] Headline is attention-grabbing
- [ ] Uses power words or numbers
- [ ] Creates curiosity or urgency
- [ ] Length is appropriate (under 30 chars ideal)
- [ ] Matches video content accurately

### Description Quality / 描述质量

- [ ] First sentence hooks attention
- [ ] Key value is communicated clearly
- [ ] CTA is specific and actionable
- [ ] Relevant hashtags included (3-5 optimal)
- [ ] Length is appropriate (not too long)

### Hashtag Strategy / 话题标签

- [ ] Mix of broad and niche tags used
- [ ] Tags are relevant to content
- [ ] Trending tags incorporated where appropriate
- [ ] Custom brand tags included
- [ ] No more than 5-7 hashtags total

### CTA Effectiveness / 行动号召

- [ ] CTA is clear and specific
- [ ] Appropriate type (follow/like/comment/share)
- [ ] Placed strategically in description
- [ ] Creates urgency or motivation
- [ ] Easy to understand and execute

---

## Script Creation Checklist / 脚本创作检查

### Structure Quality / 结构质量

- [ ] Strong hook in first 3 seconds
- [ ] Clear beginning, middle, and end
- [ ] Appropriate length for content type
- [ ] Single, focused message
- [ ] Satisfying conclusion

### Content Quality / 内容质量

- [ ] Delivers on hook's promise
- [ ] Provides real value to audience
- [ ] Authentic and relatable
- [ ] Easy to understand
- [ ] Not overly promotional

### Pacing & Flow / 节奏与流畅度

- [ ] Appropriate pacing for content type
- [ ] Transitions are smooth
- [ ] Energy is maintained throughout
- [ ] No unnecessary filler
- [ ] Builds to engaging conclusion

### Engagement Elements / 互动元素

- [ ] Encourages comments or shares
- [ ] Includes emotional hooks
- [ ] Asks questions or prompts action
- [ ] Creates shareable moments
- [ ] Relevant to target audience

---

## Production Checklist / 制作检查

### Pre-Production / 拍摄前

- [ ] Script is finalized and rehearsed
- [ ] Props and materials are ready
- [ ] Location is set and appropriate
- [ ] Outfit/appearance is prepared
- [ ] Equipment is ready (phone/camera, lighting, audio)

### During Production / 拍摄中

- [ ] Lighting is adequate and flattering
- [ ] Audio is clear and audible
- [ ] Camera is stable (or movement is intentional)
- [ ] Framing is correct
- [ ] Multiple takes for important parts

### Post-Production / 后期制作

- [ ] Footage is reviewed and best takes selected
- [ ] Editing maintains energy and pacing
- [ ] Transitions are smooth (not jarring)
- [ ] Text overlays are clear and readable
- [ ] Music/sound effects enhance (not distract)
- [ ] Color grading is consistent
- [ ] Final review before export

---

## Publishing Checklist / 发布检查

### Timing Strategy / 发布时机

- [ ] Posted during peak audience hours
- [ ] Consistent with established schedule
- [ ] Considered competitor posting times
- [ ] Aligned with content type (some content better at certain times)

### Platform Optimization / 平台优化

- [ ] Video format is correct (9:16 vertical)
- [ ] File size is appropriate
- [ ] Resolution is optimal (1080x1920)
- [ ] Caption is complete and error-free
- [ ] Cover/thumbnail is selected

### Initial Engagement / 初期互动

- [ ] Respond to first comments quickly
- [ ] Pin important comments
- [ ] Engage with similar content
- [ ] Share to other platforms if appropriate
- [ ] Monitor performance metrics

---

## Post-Publish Analysis / 发布后分析

### Performance Tracking / 表现追踪

Monitor within first 24 hours:
- [ ] View count vs. typical views
- [ ] Engagement rate (likes + comments + shares / views)
- [ ] Watch time / completion rate
- [ ] Audience retention graph
- [ ] Traffic sources

### Analysis Points / 分析要点

- [ ] What worked well?
- [ ] What could be improved?
- [ ] Any unexpected results?
- [ ] Audience feedback themes
- [ ] Lessons learned for next video

### Iteration / 迭代改进

- [ ] Document insights in content log
- [ ] Adjust future content based on learnings
- [ ] Test variations of successful elements
- [ ] Update best practices document
- [ ] Share insights with team

---

## Quality Assurance Rubric / 质量评分标准

### Excellent (5/5) - 优秀

- Hook is compelling and impossible to ignore
- Content delivers exceptional value
- Production quality is professional
- Engagement is high and authentic
- Strong brand alignment

### Good (4/5) - 良好

- Hook is interesting and relevant
- Content delivers good value
- Production quality is solid
- Engagement is good
- Clear brand alignment

### Satisfactory (3/5) - 满意

- Hook is adequate
- Content delivers some value
- Production quality is acceptable
- Engagement is moderate
- Some brand alignment

### Needs Improvement (2/5) - 需要改进

- Hook is weak or generic
- Content value is unclear
- Production quality has issues
- Low engagement
- Weak brand alignment

### Poor (1/5) - 较差

- No clear hook
- Little to no value delivered
- Significant production problems
- No engagement
- No brand alignment

---

## Quick-Fire Checklist / 快速检查清单

### 30 Seconds Before Publishing / 发布前30秒检查

- [ ] Title grabs attention?
- [ ] First 3 seconds are compelling?
- [ ] Video delivers on its promise?
- [ ] CTA is clear?
- [ ] Hashtags are relevant?
- [ ] No typos or errors?
- [ ] Posted at optimal time?
- [ ] Ready to engage with comments?

### If You Can't Say YES to All / 如果有任一项为否

→ Pause and fix before publishing!

---

## Common Mistakes to Avoid / 需避免的常见错误

### Content Mistakes / 内容错误

- [ ] No hook in first 3 seconds
- [ ] Video doesn't deliver on title's promise
- [ ] Too long without enough value
- [ ] No clear focus or message
- [ ] Overly promotional or salesy

### Production Mistakes / 制作错误

- [ ] Poor audio quality
- [ ] Bad lighting
- [ ] Shaky camera (unintentional)
- [ ] Hard to read text overlays
- [ ] Inconsistent style

### Strategy Mistakes / 策略错误

- [ ] Posting at wrong times
- [ ] Inconsistent posting schedule
- [ ] Ignoring audience feedback
- [ ] Not engaging with comments
- [ ] Copying others without differentiation

---

## Success Metrics / 成功指标

### Benchmarks by Follower Count / 粉丝数基准

| Account Size | Views Target | Engagement Rate Target |
|--------------|--------------|----------------------|
| 0-1K followers | 500+ | 15%+ |
| 1K-10K followers | 2K+ | 10%+ |
| 10K-50K followers | 10K+ | 8%+ |
| 50K-100K followers | 50K+ | 6%+ |
| 100K-500K followers | 100K+ | 5%+ |
| 500K+ followers | 200K+ | 3%+ |

### Viral Indicators / 爆款指标

A video is potentially viral if:
- [ ] Views exceed 2x your average
- [ ] Engagement rate exceeds 10%
- [ ] Shares exceed 5% of views
- [ ] Comments are active and positive
- [ ] Video appears on "For You" pages beyond followers

---

## Continuous Improvement / 持续改进

### Weekly Review Questions / 每周回顾问题

1. What was my best-performing content this week? Why?
2. What didn't perform well? Why?
3. What patterns do I notice in successful content?
4. What did my audience respond to most?
5. What should I test next week?

### Monthly Review Tasks / 每月回顾任务

- [ ] Review all content performance data
- [ ] Update audience persona based on insights
- [ ] Refine content strategy
- [ ] Identify top performing formats
- [ ] Plan content experiments for next month

---

Remember: Consistency + Authenticity + Value = Success on Douyin!
记住：一致性 + 真实性 + 价值 = 抖音成功！
